	(text "10pF loading. 5pF stray + (10pF + 10pF). Use C0G caps for stability\ncapacitor chosen using ECS tool\ncurrent-limiting resistor set to match reactance of one loading cap at frequency\nR = 1/(2pi*24MHz*10pF) = 660R"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 89.154 164.338 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "01fc1b55-a19e-4f27-a236-1e34c1e514dc")
	)
	(text "VDDA recommended decoupling is 10n + 1u (5.1.6)\nVREF+ decoupling is installed to improve ADC accuracy\nVDD decoupling recommendation is 4.7u + 100n/pin\nVDDA rail capacitance is smaller because VDDA>VDD breaks STM32\nFerrite bead helps to filter VDD switcher noise on analog ckts"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 33.782 207.264 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "11d8ce6a-bf97-4265-b446-44156ae0506d")
	)
